-- BCP's Polish unit expects Q3, Q4 net similar to Q2
-- By Marcin Goclowski
-- Mon Jul 28, 2014 04:54AM EDT
-- None



WARSAW, July 28 (Reuters) - Portuguese bank BCP's <BCP.LS> Polish unit Bank Millennium <MILP.WA> expects net profit in the third and fourth quarters similar to the 164 million zlotys ($53 million) it booked in the second, its chief executive said on Monday.

